Package: wickrabenchmark
Type: Package
Title: Reproducible Quant-Research Benchmark
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-benchmark over its C ABI hub: create a
    benchmark runner, recompute a curated case or suite with the deterministic
    Wickra engine and confirm its report and hash - the same protocol as the CLI
    and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-benchmark
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-benchmark/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-benchmark C ABI shared library (WKBENCH_LIB) and
    its header (WKBENCH_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
